BTC Trader is a crossplatform opensource live charting and technical analysis desktop application.
It is available for Windows, Linux and Mac OS X. 

This software was announced on August 2, 2011 (1.1).

## Latest version 1.4.2 includes

* Live data feed from [[Bitcoin_Charts]]
* Daily data feed from [Yahoo Finance](http://finance.yahoo.com)
* Rich collection of tech-analysis tools
> * 5 chart types
> * 8 annotation tools
> * >70 indicators

* Facebook and Twitter integration
* Automatic software updater

